Privacy Policy

Effective Date: September 9, 2025

Banking Calculator PH ("we," "our," or "us") respects your privacy. This Privacy Policy explains how we handle your information when you use our banking calculator application.

1. Information Collection

We do not collect, store, or share any personal data.

The app does not require you to create an account.

The app does not request or transmit personal information.

No analytics, cookies, or tracking technologies are used.

2. Data Storage

All information you enter into the app is stored locally on your device.

Your data never leaves your device.

We do not have access to your calculations or financial records.

If you uninstall the app or clear its data, all stored information will be permanently deleted.

3. Third-Party Services

Our app does not integrate with or share information with third parties.

4. Security

Since all information is stored locally, the security of your data depends on your device. We recommend securing your device with a password or biometric lock.

5. Children’s Privacy

Our app can be used by all ages. Since no data is collected, there are no risks of misuse of personal information.

6. Changes to This Privacy Policy

We may update this Privacy Policy from time to time. Any changes will be reflected in this document with a new “Effective Date.”

7. Contact Us

If you have any questions about this Privacy Policy, you may contact us at: abusyday007@gmail.com
